      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王氏上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00002",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "嗯哼。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00003",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "我们当家的不在家，终朝每日思想他。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00004",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "我，王氏。配夫张三，是个小买卖人，也不是铜匠，也不是铁匠。是他妈个银匠。娶了我三天，一去三年，也没有音信回来。我去年六月里，替他养了一个儿子。我母子每日纺棉花度日。看今日天气晴和，不免纺棉花便了。",
      "text_length": 98
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00005",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小孩哭。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00006",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "你看，我不作活，我儿子也不哭；我一作活，他就哭呢。儿子儿子不要哭，妈妈来呢。不要哭呢，吃点尖罢。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00007",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "儿子儿子你不要哭，妈妈与你买个皮老虎。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00008",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "你看不要他哭，他偏哭，你哭你哭，滚你妈的蛋！待我纺棉花便了。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00009",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "王氏女坐草堂自思自叹，思想起我儿夫好不惨然。他去贸易未回转，倒叫我二八女挂在心间。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00010",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张三上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00011",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "一日离家一日深，好似孤雁宿寒林。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00012",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "我，张三。出外贸易三年，算清帐目，回家探问妻子便了。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00013",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "急急忙忙往前进，不觉来到自家门。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00014",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "到呢，门是那个门，人不晓得可是那个人么？待我来叫门。慢着，我出外三年，不晓得我这个老婆，在家作些甚么事，待我来听听看。",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00015",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "哦吓，我今天纺棉花纺得高兴；如其不然，我唱一个小曲与你们老爷们听听。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00016",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "呀，我离家三年，她倒会唱小曲了！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00017",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "你们要是爱听呢，我就唱；你们要不爱听，那我就不唱。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00018",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "他们老爷不爱听，我还要听呢。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00019",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "那么我就唱一个，唱一个。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00020",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "那么我听一个，听一个。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00021",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "我唱吧。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00022",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "我听吧。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00023",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "唱吧。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00024",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "听吧。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00025",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "思调",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "一双红绣鞋，哎哎呀，正月里水仙花儿开，哎哎呀；三窖的萝卜还在那窖里埋，哎哎呀，你说冻了心，我的那个小乖乖，哎哎呀。二双红绣鞋，哎哎呀，二月里杏花开，哎哎呀；小小的顽童吃的什么长寿斋呀，你说开了吧，我的那个小郎才，哎哎呀。",
      "text_length": 110
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00026",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "好，唱的真不错，待我来叫门。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00027",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "我今天唱得高兴，再唱一个。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00028",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "我今天听得高兴，再听一个吧。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00029",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "我再唱一个，再唱一个吧。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00030",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "我再听一个，听一个吧。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00031",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "唱吧。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00032",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "听吧。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00033",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "思调",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "姐在房中绣麒麟，忽然间想起了我们那个心上的人。常常我就挂在心，呀唗呔咦，常常奴就挂在心，哎哎呀。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00034",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "好！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00035",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "思调",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "奴在娘家，你常常来往，一到了婆婆家，你就不登奴的门。情郎哥哥你就又有别人，呀唗呔咦，情郎哥哥你就相交别人，哎哎呀。",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00036",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "好，待我来叫门。慢着，我不放心。再听听看。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00037",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "我今个越唱越高兴。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00038",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "我今个越听越高兴。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00039",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "唱一个，唱一个吧。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00040",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "听一个，听一吧。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00041",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "唱吧。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00042",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "听吧。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00043",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "思调",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "正月里来锣鼓敲，思想前妻好不心焦。去年与你同欢乐，欢天喜地过元宵。开开了门往外瞧，对对的佳人把花灯闹。鳏棍掉了那个伤心的泪，结发的妻子哪里去了？哎咳呀，哎咳呀，人来吧，人来吧！",
      "text_length": 88
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00044",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "唱得真好，待我来叫门。慢着，我还不放心，再听听看。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00045",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "我再唱一个吧。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00046",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "我再听一个吧。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00047",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "唱吧。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00048",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "听吧",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00049",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "思调",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "妓女好悲伤，哎哎呀，一阵我们心内慌，哎哎呀。伤心埋怨二老爹娘，最不该你将奴卖至在烟花巷，哎哎呀。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00050",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "唱的真不错，待我在来敲门。慢着，我到底不放心，再来听听看。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00051",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "思调",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "姐在房中哭，姐在房中哭，哭来哭去哭他的丈夫。为什么真真哭，为什么真真哭？怕的是她丈夫卖了屁股，哎哎呀。",
      "text_length": 51
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00052",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "咦，我在外头卖了屁股，她怎么晓得的？待我进去问问她。不要忙，我再听听看。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00053",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "干板",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "纺纺棉花，四两棉花都纺定，但等明天住娘家。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00054",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "咦，我不回家，她也不住娘家；我刚刚回来，她又要住娘家。不对，我出去三年，不晓得怎么度日？我不免拿块砖头扔进去，看她说什么。",
      "text_length": 61
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00055",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张三扔砖头，王氏接砖头。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00056",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "呀，什么东西响？待我拿灯来照照。咦，原来是块砖头。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00057",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "哽，砖头。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00058",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "谁扔的？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00059",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "我。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00060",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "我告诉你吧，你也不打听打听！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00061",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "打听什么？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00062",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "太太臂膊上能跑马，脊梁上能行车，捺一刀冒紫血，加等等的好朋友，七蛋不够，八蛋造的，接砖头！",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00063",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王氏扔砖头。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00064",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "呀，够朋友，待我来叫门。慢着，砖头她扔出来了，待我拿银子试试她，要扔出来，就够朋友；她不扔出来就不够朋友，接银子！",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00065",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张三扔银子。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00066",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "呀，又是什么东西扔进来了？待我拿灯来照照。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00067",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "银子。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00068",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "哦，原来是锭银子，谁扔的？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00069",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "我。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00070",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "哦，不要是这边老三吧？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00071",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "你们谁是老三。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00072",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "老三呀，老三，你这就不该，知道你哥哥不在家，跑在这调戏你嫂子来呢！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00073",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "不错。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00074",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "我告诉你，你这锭银子，你可扔进来，我可不能与你扔出去呢！明天拿到街上买衣裳，打首饰，买花戴，管叫你闻香不到口，谗得你满街走，我睡觉去呢，咱们明天见！",
      "text_length": 74
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00075",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "够朋友，待我来叫门。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00076",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "慢着。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00077",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "不好。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00078",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "常言说的好，得人钱财与人消灾。反正我们当家的不在家，这碗冷饭，我偷呢吃了吧。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00079",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "不好。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00080",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "老三，老三，你不要走，嫂子这里开门呢。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00081",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王氏开门。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00082",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "贱人无礼无礼，不该你偷吃冷饭！恨不得一拳打死你，你给我死你给我死！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00083",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "谁呀？呀，原来是我们那口子，他回来了。待我来问问他。我说你不是张三么？",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00084",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "我是张三，还是李四呢！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00085",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "你几时回来的？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00086",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "你唱小曲那会回来的。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00087",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "那块砖头谁扔的？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00088",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "我扔的。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00089",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "太太骂出去没有？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00090",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "骂出去够朋友，那锭银子呢？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00091",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "银子我告诉你，你去的三年，一个钱不往家里带，叫我吃什么，喝什么，难道说你的银子我就用不得？",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00092",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "银子用得，我问你那个老三是谁？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00093",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 93,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "老三呢，哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00094",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 94,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "你给我死，你给我死！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00095",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 95,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "这怎么好，待我拿儿子哄哄他吧！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00096",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 96,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王氏抱孩子。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00097",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 97,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "儿子，你爸爸来了，看看他吧。我说你过来，你去了三年，我去年六月，给你养了一个儿子。你抱了去吧！",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00098",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 98,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "什么？我去了三年，你去年六月里。给我养了一个儿子。这个儿子我不晓得打哪里来的，我也不要！",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00099",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 99,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "你不要，我就扔掉他，我寻死了。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00100",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 100,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "好呢。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00101",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 101,
      "seq_in_scene": 101,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，天吓，我出家去了！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00102",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 102,
      "seq_in_scene": 102,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "好呢，你不要哭了，我们夫妻团圆，睡觉去吧。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00103",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 103,
      "seq_in_scene": 103,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "我不去。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00104",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 104,
      "seq_in_scene": 104,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "你不去，我就要……",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00105",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 105,
      "seq_in_scene": 105,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "你要怎么样？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00106",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 106,
      "seq_in_scene": 106,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "我要跪下呢。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00107",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 107,
      "seq_in_scene": 107,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "老三，你来吧。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00108",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 108,
      "seq_in_scene": 108,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "慢着，我去了三年，是谁照应她？叫她回来问问。家里的，你回来。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00109",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 109,
      "seq_in_scene": 109,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "干什么？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00110",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 110,
      "seq_in_scene": 110,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "我问你，我去了三年，家里头谁照应的？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00111",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 111,
      "seq_in_scene": 111,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "照应我的人多得很，上上下下都是的。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00112",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 112,
      "seq_in_scene": 112,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "有这么些人来，这屋里头挤不下，你到底有个准的？",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00113",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 113,
      "seq_in_scene": 113,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "准的有一个。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00114",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 114,
      "seq_in_scene": 114,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00115",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 115,
      "seq_in_scene": 115,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "你顺着我手看，就是那个戴金丝眼镜的！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00116",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 116,
      "seq_in_scene": 116,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王氏下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00117",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 117,
      "seq_in_scene": 117,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张三"
      ],
      "text": "对不住，对不住！我的家主婆承你照应，明朝请你一枝香吃大菜！得罪，得罪！",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01007016_e00118",
      "play_id": "01007016",
      "scene_id": "01007016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 118,
      "seq_in_scene": 118,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张三下。",
      "text_length": 4
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}